venings and weekends</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and therefore, particularly in the early years of a child’s life</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, most STEM professionals</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> strive to find a balance where</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> one or </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">other parent is </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">regularly </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">available </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">during the child’s waking hours </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">to provide </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">a secure and loving environment. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">It is more often than not the female parent who takes a career break to facilitate this.</span></h1><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="5" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.25pt; padding-left:4.75pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Data from</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">n internal</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> survey of current and recent</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> past </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Ro